:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"依家姐係點，兩個一齊壓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係剩係咕咕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e52a6d38026a570a2fece040aabd0432079b41","tid":274234,"uid":14347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家姐係點，兩個一齊壓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係剩係咕咕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咕咕死應該都會壓埋落黎掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死前仲講咩兄弟的含義，不死真係好撚慘"},{"pid":"4e9e87e267550c76f89e2853db80ccdf5d4bc0d3","tid":274234,"uid":107623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好睇過聲之形</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話</blockquote><br />\n唔同意，聲之形由頭到尾好完整。而且作為有遇/參與過欺凌事件嘅人去睇依套作品，果啲感覺係完全無辦法比擬。<br />\n<br />\n而且依套始終未完。"},{"pid":"7f701a0717e6fa99456925aa9518552101316a18","tid":274234,"uid":29442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好睇過聲之形</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話</blockquote><br />\n唔同意，聲之形由頭到尾好完整。而且作為有遇/參與過欺凌事件嘅人去睇依套作品，果啲感覺係完全無辦法比擬。<br />\n<br />\n而且依套始終未完。</blockquote><br />\n聲之形結尾係完整 但係開頭做得太好 結尾既水準同開頭差好遠<br />\n<br />\n不過你岩 呢套仲未完 唔好咁早落定論住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852502d76b0962a646306c40c53a81a2675c2210","tid":274234,"uid":93351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"已經SAD左兩個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次比個好結局 比咕咕同玲玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13992ce87a60c7ba7c2b421356d92105cc85e05","tid":274234,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:29:20.000Z","msg